description: The associated files are mass spec data from size exclusion chromatography fractions that were subsequently crosslinked with DSSO and digested with one of two enzymes, Trypsin or Chymotrypsin.  The starting material was a native extract prepared from Chlamydomonas reinhardtii.  The mass spectrometry used a data-dependent MS2-MS3 method to identify crosslinks.
